snippet.title: Best VGM 2287 - Bomberman 64 : The Second Attack - Planet Select
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

N64
Bomberman 64 : The Second Attack (1999)
Planet Select
Yasunori Mitsuda
